metadata.name: Plastic Babyheads from Outer Space
metadata.description: The conclusion of The Cave of Forgotten Comedians! Deep in the cave, the Stooge Pies have freed a beautiful woman held captive by a strange religious cult led by the most annoying comedian of all-time! Together with the dazzling Bella Dilemma, can they foil the comedian’s diabolical schemes to conquer Hollywood -- and the world?
